            "color_hint": null,
            "position_hint": null,
            "duration_s": 3.0
          },
          {
            "id": "step_2",
            "description": "粒子进入磁场并偏转。粒子从L2进入，画出半圆轨迹，最终垂直穿过L3。",
            "targets": [
              "trajectory_B1",
              "particle"
